減持排名前五的公司：<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com/20200215000449843938fe1f9ec.png/logo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F20200215000449843938fe1f9ec.png%2Flogo&h=57b62e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">高瓴資本</span></div></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中概股佔據了前十大重倉股中的六個席位</span>。整體來看,愛奇藝連續三個季度成為高瓴資本第一大重倉股,前五大重倉股分別是愛奇藝、百濟神州、Align科技、好未來和ZOOM<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RhAG6LR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRhAG6LR.png&h=a44bbbe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網公司依然受高瓴青睞,<span style=\"color: red;\">愛奇藝、阿里巴巴、京東和拼多多仍然坐穩前十大重倉股的位置</span>。其中阿里巴巴少量減持後仍持有近200萬股,持有市值達到4.2億美元,這四家互聯網公司的累計持有市值超過21億美元,由此可見高瓴依然看重新經濟對市場和社會所帶來的巨大改變,以及蘊含其中的投資機會。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">老虎環球</span></div></span></strong><br />\n老虎環球Q4持倉總市值為181.22億美元，上一季度總市值為189美元，環比下降約4.1%。本季度，老虎環球在持倉組合中新增了5只標的，增持15只標的。<br />\n<br />\n從持倉偏好來看，老虎環球持有的信息技術類股票占整個投資組合的比重最大，但<span style=\"color: red;\">所持有的消費及通訊、科技類股各佔比重與之相差不大</span>。<br />\n<br />\n四季度，<a href=\"http://老虎環球新建倉兩隻信息技術類股基於雲的領先軟件提供商Bill.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%80%81%E8%99%8E%E7%92%B0%E7%90%83%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA%E5%80%89%E5%85%A9%E9%9A%BB%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E9%A1%9E%E8%82%A1%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%BC%E9%9B%B2%E7%9A%84%E9%A0%98%E5%85%88%E8%BB%9F%E4%BB%B6%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%95%86Bill.com&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=ea9fbd7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">老虎環球新建倉兩隻信息技術類股基於雲的領先軟件提供商Bill.com</a> Holdings及消費數據供應商Cardlytics Inc、兩隻科技股谷歌母公司Alpabet 及PayPal、一隻金融股巴西金融服務公司。<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com//tmp/phpG2XtQz.jpg/big\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F%2Ftmp%2FphpG2XtQz.jpg%2Fbig&h=87c38c71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四季度，老虎環球在明星股阿里巴巴的持股比例縮減達到54%；Spotify的持股比例縮減14%；NetFlix的持股比例縮減27%；Facebook的持股比例縮減25%；亞馬遜的持股比例縮減13%。<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com//tmp/phpU2bwhZ.jpg/big\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F%2Ftmp%2FphpU2bwhZ.jpg%2Fbig&h=0bba40e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com//tmp/phpMNn6PW.jpg/big\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F%2Ftmp%2FphpMNn6PW.jpg%2Fbig&h=d8297615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前五大重倉股中，京東佔比10.2744%排名第一，阿波羅全球管理佔比9.9158%排名第二，微軟排名第三，Facebook排名第四，TransDigm Group排名第五。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知LIHK仔對巴老既投資有咩建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:42:24.000Z","msg":"巴打，邊度可以塭到依D資料?<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f49c9331fa295e898c0c17b54a5312116737cc","tid":1880840,"uid":8439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:55:29.000Z","msg":"巴老都要買etf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f635184f7faad8739bb2b128decdc11d899881","tid":1880840,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab0ba37ae5dbf681b339d5d83f9aa07d5249226b","tid":1880840,"uid":81889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de9587a388ca282ea0bd584703c69ca09f7d8a3c","tid":1880840,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:58:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">巴郡</span></div></span></strong><br />\nQ4總規模2420.51億美元，環比增加了12.75%。在報告期內，巴郡減持了8家公司，同時增持了4家公司，新買入​​4家公司/ETF。具體來看，這次主要變化有：<br />\n<br />\n減持蘋果，但仍是第一大重倉股<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com/2020021500044980bee694aa328.png/logo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F2020021500044980bee694aa328.png%2Flogo&h=6d2d4389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴郡減持近1.5%的蘋果股份，年底持股數量約2.45億股，市值約720億美元；<span style=\"color: red;\">蘋果占伯克希爾總持倉的29.74%，仍為第一大重倉股</span>。<br />\n<br />\n減持8個標的，5個為金融股<br />\n<br />\n巴郡減持了包括富國銀行、美國銀行、高盛銀行等金融股。這是為了<span style=\"color: red;\">避免股權超過10%，引起監管機構的審查</span>。巴郡在前兩者的持股接近10%的水平，不過高盛銀行僅持股3.4%。<br />\n巴郡Q4減持的8家公司中，有5家屬於金融行業。不過值得一提的是，摩根大通和美國合眾銀行持倉並無變動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com/20200215000449813c25c3de071.png/logo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F20200215000449813c25c3de071.png%2Flogo&h=88dcf5cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下圖展示了伯克希爾2019年四季度買入和減持排名前五的公司：<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com/20200215000449843938fe1f9ec.png/logo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F20200215000449843938fe1f9ec.png%2Flogo&h=57b62e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">高瓴資本</span></div></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中概股佔據了前十大重倉股中的六個席位</span>。整體來看,愛奇藝連續三個季度成為高瓴資本第一大重倉股,前五大重倉股分別是愛奇藝、百濟神州、Align科技、好未來和ZOOM<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RhAG6LR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRhAG6LR.png&h=a44bbbe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網公司依然受高瓴青睞,<span style=\"color: red;\">愛奇藝、阿里巴巴、京東和拼多多仍然坐穩前十大重倉股的位置</span>。其中阿里巴巴少量減持後仍持有近200萬股,持有市值達到4.2億美元,這四家互聯網公司的累計持有市值超過21億美元,由此可見高瓴依然看重新經濟對市場和社會所帶來的巨大改變,以及蘊含其中的投資機會。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">老虎環球</span></div></span></strong><br />\n老虎環球Q4持倉總市值為181.22億美元，上一季度總市值為189美元，環比下降約4.1%。本季度，老虎環球在持倉組合中新增了5只標的，增持15只標的。<br />\n<br />\n從持倉偏好來看，老虎環球持有的信息技術類股票占整個投資組合的比重最大，但<span style=\"color: red;\">所持有的消費及通訊、科技類股各佔比重與之相差不大</span>。<br />\n<br />\n四季度，<a href=\"http://老虎環球新建倉兩隻信息技術類股基於雲的領先軟件提供商Bill.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%80%81%E8%99%8E%E7%92%B0%E7%90%83%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA%E5%80%89%E5%85%A9%E9%9A%BB%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E9%A1%9E%E8%82%A1%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%BC%E9%9B%B2%E7%9A%84%E9%A0%98%E5%85%88%E8%BB%9F%E4%BB%B6%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%95%86Bill.com&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=ea9fbd7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">老虎環球新建倉兩隻信息技術類股基於雲的領先軟件提供商Bill.com</a> Holdings及消費數據供應商Cardlytics Inc、兩隻科技股谷歌母公司Alpabet 及PayPal、一隻金融股巴西金融服務公司。<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com//tmp/phpG2XtQz.jpg/big\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F%2Ftmp%2FphpG2XtQz.jpg%2Fbig&h=87c38c71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四季度，老虎環球在明星股阿里巴巴的持股比例縮減達到54%；Spotify的持股比例縮減14%；NetFlix的持股比例縮減27%；Facebook的持股比例縮減25%；亞馬遜的持股比例縮減13%。<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com//tmp/phpU2bwhZ.jpg/big\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F%2Ftmp%2FphpU2bwhZ.jpg%2Fbig&h=0bba40e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com//tmp/phpMNn6PW.jpg/big\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F%2Ftmp%2FphpMNn6PW.jpg%2Fbig&h=d8297615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前五大重倉股中，京東佔比10.2744%排名第一，阿波羅全球管理佔比9.9158%排名第二，微軟排名第三，Facebook排名第四，TransDigm Group排名第五。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知LIHK仔對巴老既投資有咩建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:42:24.000Z","msg":"巴打，邊度可以塭到依D資料?<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:03:21.000Z","msg":"中資富途出既文黎嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢D有曬數據既野冇立場<br />\n俾廣大學生/FG/新手入美股既了解吓市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed6769cae55a1abd4c360755a92bcba33b1155e","tid":1880840,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b197312b4a875aeb8f3763b0df6c47bc7720358","tid":1880840,"uid":76855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77ae75291b9ac6530c87b6d721a49dc1962860f7","tid":1880840,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:44:27.000Z","msg":"大家都開始擴散落去搵小型雲計算股搏高回報<br />\n<br />\nMega cap相對顯得冇咁擠擁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:47:26.000Z","msg":"其實RNG 同ZOOM 有乜特別，覺得佢值搏既人係用咩角度去睇？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea5d94134e40e15f12a82c0e346776cda3a08c1","tid":1880840,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ed6769cae55a1abd4c360755a92bcba33b1155e","tid":1880840,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b197312b4a875aeb8f3763b0df6c47bc7720358","tid":1880840,"uid":76855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77ae75291b9ac6530c87b6d721a49dc1962860f7","tid":1880840,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:44:27.000Z","msg":"大家都開始擴散落去搵小型雲計算股搏高回報<br />\n<br />\nMega cap相對顯得冇咁擠擁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:47:26.000Z","msg":"其實RNG 同ZOOM 有乜特別，覺得佢值搏既人係用咩角度去睇？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e700f51bdbb0c81cb2f72569d9fd24d9a13caac2","tid":1880840,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:13:59.000Z","msg":"